{
  "texts": [
    "The author has explored Urdu Named Entity Recognition algorithm using RBA that outperforms the models used by statistical machine learning for IJCNLP 2008 which contains only 36,000 words in Urdu.",
    "Sharipov et al. [63] presented the tagger tool and annotated dataset of POS for the limited resources of Uzbek language and dataset contains 12 tags which is used to develop tagger tool and POS using RBA.",
    "The author also presented new dataset for tagger tool that contains more than 1500 sentences with overall accuracy of 90% which is used for natural language processing techniques such as machine translation etc.",
    "Salah et al. [64] suggested an approach on trigger patterns, words, rules and gazetteers generated from linguistic data regarding entities with Arabic names.",
    "The approach contains are processing the rule application stage, preprocessing stage and operational stage."
  ]
}